MephistoFeedback
================

This mephisto plugin provides a mechanism for submitting feedback.

Just create a static page, set the Format to "Plain HTML", and paste this into it:

<h3 id="respond">Send us feedback</h3>
<form method="POST" id="comment-form" action="/feedback">
  <p><input type="text" id="comment_author" name="feedback[name]" value="" /><label for="author"><small>Name</small></label></p>
  <p><input type="text" id="comment_author_email" name="feedback[email]" value="" /><label for="email"><small>Mail</small></label></p>
 <input type="hidden" name="feedback[key]" value="feedback" />
  <p><textarea name="feedback[body]" id="comment" cols="100%" rows="10"></textarea></p>
  <p><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" value="Submit Feedback" /></p>
</form>

Save, and link.

That's it, you now have a feedback form.

Feel free to embelish.